review_title: Not as baggy but still comfy and cute!
reviews: Super cute, colour is the same as the picture, not quite as baggy as it is in the picture though. Pockets are very large which is awesome
Looks just like photo and surprisingly well made! Nice size and pretty easy to assemble. Shipping was also super fast, I have no complaints.
Bought a 33ft string of fairy lights and bought these to put them up. The string clips in perfectly and you can barely see them! They come with extra adhesive strips and plenty of clips
Great product for price, seems pretty accurate so far, it doesn’t change every time I step on the scale.
Definitely worth the cheap price! Easy to use makes applying face masks much easier and cleaner

Absolutely love this jacket! Would recommend ordering a size up if you want it looser like in the pic but good thick real denim material. POCKETS ARE FAKE! I’m 5’2 120 lbs bought a large and it’s fits a bit baggy on me so I can easily fit sweaters under it
Fits perfectly, super comfortable, pockets are awesome and they stay up! I’m 5,2 120lbs bought medium in these as well as other colours and also capris they fit perfect

Great product super comfy. I think they may be on the smaller size for men so if you’re a dude probably order a size up. I’m a 5’2 120lbs woman, ordered a large and it’s a perfectly baggy! Definitely worth it!
Soft and comfortable great product for price. Can be used alone or with cover

Awesome product looks just like the picture and was super fast shipping! The size is off by maybe an inch or 2 but overall definitely worth the price. Customer service was great too responded fast and was super helpful :)

Looks amazing I love these! They were easy to install, only took about 25/30 min all together. On my drivers side light sometimes I get a hyper blink but I think that’s a wiring issue from my Jeep and not the product itself

review_title: Fits awesome and looks just like picture
reviews: Fits awesome and looks just like picture. The only problem is when you open the console the back edge comes off.
Great product looks awesome. Install is simple, but easier said than done. These give the Jeep a subtle put together look
Looks awesome, works great, fast delivery right on time and good pricing.

This is honestly quite a steal to get this game at this low of a price and in such great condition. It's a really fun game, and though it didn't come with its original case I could care less, I got it to play, not to look pretty on my shelf
Great price, fast and easy delivery, and a very fun game!

In perfect condition and very fast delivery. Got it the very first day of expected delivery. The game is also super fun, and it's even better that it's a 3 person game! It's awesome to play by yourself but even better to be able to have the option to play with your friends as well! And the most important part is that it's incredibly cheap!
The game looks like it's factory fresh, there's not a single thing wrong with the game, especially for its amazing price! Also I received the product on the very first day of the estimated shipping!
